\newlabel{fig:individual_pr}{{11}{15}{Per-topic PR curves for KNN(MedCPT) on all 33 test topics. Green = best topic (170 --- isoniazid hepatotoxicity, AP=0.8961); red = worst topic (140 --- spontaneous hand fractures, AP=0.1168); orange = median topic (120 --- causes of facial numbness, AP=0.6277). Gray curves = remaining 30 topics. Dashed navy = mean AP (MAP=0.6143)}{figure.11}{}}
